code: @Override public Object get(String name, ObjectFactory<?> objectFactory) {     Object mutex = RequestContextHolder.currentRequestAttributes().getSessionMutex().     synchronized (mutex) {         return super.get(name, objectFactory).     } }

@Override @Nullable public Object remove(String name) {     Object mutex = RequestContextHolder.currentRequestAttributes().getSessionMutex().     synchronized (mutex) {         return super.remove(name).     } }
